          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Student and Teacher Safety Act of </b><strong>2022</strong></p> <p>This bill allows local educational agencies to use certain federal funds for activities related to school safety, including infrastructure improvements to prevent, mitigate, or respond to incidents of school violence.</p>]]>
